videos.description: Jerrion Ealy takes the handoff and plows his way through traffic to score a short 1-yard touchdown to give Ole Miss an early. 6-0 lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Jerrion Ealy puts Ole Miss up early with short TD) 2021/09/06 ESHEET

videos.headline: Jerrion Ealy puts Ole Miss up early with short TD

videos.description: Monty Montgomery is ejected from the game on a targeting call after a helmet-to-helmet collision with Matt Corral.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Louisville's Monty Montgomery ejected for targeting) 2021/09/06 ESHEET

videos.headline: Louisville's Monty Montgomery ejected for targeting

videos.description: Matt Corral shows off his agility as he navigates through traffic to score a 6-yard touchdown for Ole Miss.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Matt Corral races to score 6-yard TD) 2021/09/06 ESHEET

videos.headline: Matt Corral races to score 6-yard TD

videos.description: Ole Miss's Mark Robinson is ejected from the game after a targeting call at the end of the first quarter.

videos.headline: Ole Miss's Mark Robinson gets ejected after big hit

videos.description: Malik Cunningham throws a pass into traffic and Louisville's Deantre Prince leaps to get the interception.

videos.headline: Deantre Prince picks off Malik Cunningham's pass

videos.description: Snoop Conner takes the handoff and works his way through defenders to score a short 1-yard touchdown to put Ole Miss up 23-0.

videos.headline: Snoop Conner plows his way to Ole Miss TD

videos.description: Louisville's Monty Montgomery and Tabarius Peterson and Ole Miss' Mark Robinson and Lakia Henry are all ejected from the game on separate targeting calls in the first half.

videos.headline: Four players ejected for targeting in 1st half of Ole Miss vs. Louisville

videos.headline: Braden Smith makes the catch for Louisville TD

videos.description: Snoop Conner bowls over a Louisville defender as he reaches the end zone to score an 11-yard Ole Miss touchdown.

videos.headline: Snoop Conner bulldozes his way to Ole Miss TD

videos.description: A fan's dog in the stands gets up in excitement as Malik Cunningham rushes in to score a 1-yard touchdown for Louisville.

videos.headline: Dog gets excited in the stands for Louisville TD
